title: Louis Vuitton Diamier Papillon 26
description: Louis Vuitton Papillon 26 in Damier coated canvas. Featuring gold-toned hardware, brown leather trim and dual flat top handles. The top zipper opens to a red canvas lining interior. Approximate dimensions: 26cm(L) x 13.5cm(H) x 13.5cm(D), handle drop 12cm. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
